{"TopicId":138611,"ForumId":16,"TopicTitle":"Adjust mousewheel acceleration for editing maneuver nodes?","CreatedByName":"qeveren","CreatedById":10381,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-05-01T01:43:44Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"qeveren","CreatedById":10381,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-05-01T01:43:44Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIs there a way to set (or disable) the mousewheel acceleration when fine-tuning maneuver nodes?\u00A0 It feels like the acceleration curve is way too steep: one tick, hardly any change; two ticks, still hardly any change; three in rapid sequence, huge glob of delta-v. \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:D\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"blorgon","CreatedById":159569,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-05-01T01:51:00Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI always found that pretty annoying.\u00A0Any particular reason you don\u0027t want to use Precise Node?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-05-01T01:51:21Z\u0022 title=\u002205/01/2016 01:51  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00228 yr\u0022\u003EMay 1, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by blorgon\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"qeveren","CreatedById":10381,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-05-01T02:19:58Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222552019\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022138611\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221462067460\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022159569\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022blorgon\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n28 minutes ago, blorgon said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI always found that pretty annoying.\u00A0Any particular reason you don\u0027t want to use Precise Node?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWell... I guess I might have to, now that I know it\u0027s a thing. \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:D\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"OutlawFarmer","CreatedById":160886,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-05-01T09:46:08Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf you scroll down instead of up it makes a smaller change\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}